title: This weird cat loves his beer box but hates his tail more than anything in the world
text:
Cats are weird and stupid. Don't argue, just accept it.
Evidence supporting this argument? Maras here, who is as stupid as he is cute but unfortunately that makes him quite stupid when it comes to not realising his tail belongs to him and not another creature.
Via YouTube
